<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 18:14:15 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国议员敦促大众汽车退出新疆业务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/us-lawmakers-urge-vw-exit-xinjiang-operations-2024-02-22/</link><description>美国众议院中国问题委员会主席和该委员会的民主党高层敦促大众汽车停止在新疆的业务，此前数千辆装有中国制造的小型电子元件的汽车被扣押在美国港口。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 16:45:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/us-lawmakers-urge-vw-exit-xinjiang-operations-2024-02-22/</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰战争已过去两年，全球贸易裂痕扩大</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-trade-rift-widening-ukraine-war-passes-two-year-mark-2024-02-22/</link><description>俄罗斯入侵乌克兰两年后，有明显迹象表明全球经济正在分裂成两个独立的集团，近 30 年来支撑商业的多边贸易规则正受到威胁。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 14:25:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-trade-rift-widening-ukraine-war-passes-two-year-mark-2024-02-22/</guid></item><item><title>海德堡材料考虑在美国上市以解决估值差距</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/heidelberg-materials-weighs-us-listing-tackle-valuation-gap-2024-02-22/</link><description>海德堡材料公司首席执行官周四对分析师表示，该公司正在考虑在美国上市，以此作为潜在解决估值地域差距的一种方式。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 14:22:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/heidelberg-materials-weighs-us-listing-tackle-valuation-gap-2024-02-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动卡车初创公司Windrose首席执行官表示探索在欧洲生产</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-electric-truck-start-up-windrose-explores-production-europe-ceo-says-2024-02-22/</link><description>中国电动重型卡车初创公司Windrose的创始人兼首席执行官周四表示，该公司计划将其车辆的制造外包给欧洲的汽车制造合作伙伴，以寻求在该地区与特斯拉和梅赛德斯奔驰的竞争对手展开竞争。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 11:52:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-electric-truck-start-up-windrose-explores-production-europe-ceo-says-2024-02-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国要求国际法院就以色列“非法”占领发表言论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-asks-world-court-speak-out-unlawful-israeli-occupation-2024-02-22/</link><description>中国周四要求国际法院就以色列占领巴勒斯坦领土发表意见，称以色列占领巴勒斯坦领土是非法的。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 11:51:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-asks-world-court-speak-out-unlawful-israeli-occupation-2024-02-22/</guid></item><item><title>英伟达首席执行官表示，已开始为中国市场提供两款新的人工智能芯片样品</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/nvidia-has-begun-sampling-two-new-ai-chips-china-market-says-ceo-2024-02-22/</link><description>英伟达首席执行官黄仁勋表示，英伟达目前正在向客户提供两款针对中国市场的新型人工智能芯片样品，以捍卫其在目前受到美国出口限制威胁的中国市场主导地位。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 11:23:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/nvidia-has-begun-sampling-two-new-ai-chips-china-market-says-ceo-2024-02-22/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：人工智能“临界点”推动英伟达、纳斯达克、日经指数走高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-02-22/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 11:04:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-02-22/</guid></item><item><title>梅赛德斯首席执行官警告欧盟不要针对中国采取保护主义</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-ceo-warns-eu-against-protectionism-response-china-2024-02-22/</link><description>梅赛德斯-奔驰首席执行官奥拉·卡林纽斯周四在汽车制造商公布季度业绩后表示，欧盟针对中国加强保护主义的任何举措，对于欧洲等经济地区来说都是破坏性的举动。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 10:50:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-ceo-warns-eu-against-protectionism-response-china-2024-02-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国将向美国派遣更多大熊猫 开启“熊猫外交”新时代</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-send-more-pandas-us-jump-starting-new-era-panda-diplomacy-2024-02-22/</link><description>中国野生动物保护协会正在与华盛顿国家动物园合作，安排将更多大熊猫带回美国，这标志着两个超级大国之间的外交关系正在改善。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 10:34:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-send-more-pandas-us-jump-starting-new-era-panda-diplomacy-2024-02-22/</guid></item><item><title>臭气熏天的塞尔维亚废水加剧了环境问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/smelly-serbian-wastewater-adds-environmental-woes-2024-02-22/</link><description>在贝尔格莱德高档滨水区的一栋新建高层建筑旁边，一条恶臭的溪流将污水直接排入萨瓦河，萨瓦河是污染该市水域的数十个排水口之一。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 08:37:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/smelly-serbian-wastewater-adds-environmental-woes-2024-02-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国科考船在印度洋作业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-research-vessels-operating-indian-ocean-2024-02-22/</link><description>中国的科学调查船队正在不断壮大，尽管政府坚称这些船只仅用于研究目的，但一些亚洲邻国，尤其是印度，担心他们收集的敏感数据可能会与中国军方分享。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 07:34:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-research-vessels-operating-indian-ocean-2024-02-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国商飞在新加坡航展上抢走了空客和波音的风头</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinese-planemaker-comac-upstages-airbus-boeing-singapore-airshow-2024-02-22/</link><description>中国国有飞机制造商中国商飞公司本周在新加坡航展上抢走了行业领头羊空客和波音公司的风头，在寻求国际认证和外国订单的同时，展示了其自主研发的C919和ARJ21喷气式飞机。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 07:23:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinese-planemaker-comac-upstages-airbus-boeing-singapore-airshow-2024-02-22/</guid></item><item><title>法国食品集团达能对 2023 年的强劲表现充满信心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/french-food-group-danone-confident-over-2024-sales-after-stellar-2023-2024-02-22/</link><description>法国食品集团达能周四表示，继去年销售增长达到预期上限后，公司对未来一年充满信心，因为价格上涨提高了利润率，抵消了销量下降的影响。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 06:23:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/french-food-group-danone-confident-over-2024-sales-after-stellar-2023-2024-02-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国联想营收在连续五个季度下滑后实现增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-lenovo-posts-revenue-growth-after-five-quarters-decline-2024-02-22/</link><description>全球最大的个人电脑 (PC) 制造商中国联想集团周四公布了强于预期的收益，其收入在经历了 5 个季度的下滑后恢复增长，原因是新冠肺炎 (COVID-19) 疫情过后经济放缓。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 05:38:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-lenovo-posts-revenue-growth-after-five-quarters-decline-2024-02-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国面临更大的压力，要求采取重大政策来修复经济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/pressure-grows-china-big-policy-moves-fix-economy-2024-02-22/</link><description>随着下个月中国人大年度会议的临近，中国领导人面临着近十年来最大的压力，需要做出大胆的政策决定，以保障经济的长期增长潜力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 05:36:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/pressure-grows-china-big-policy-moves-fix-economy-2024-02-22/</guid></item></channel></rss>